article_title: Obamacare Costs Slow, Choices Abound In New Open Enrollment

article_metadata.description: The Affordable Care Act and its recalibrated healthcare.gov web site forges ahead this week with many consumers preparing to buy plans insurers report will be at a “lower cost” than last year and with more choices. A new study from a nonpartisan group and information from health insurer earnings reports indicate [...]
